    "created_at": "2012-10-19T05:54:34Z",
    "updated_at": "2012-10-19T05:54:34Z",
    "body": "I think the approach in that comment is obsolete with pipes. Now I prefer changing the task notification to a `pipes::OneShot` (with a different name), and have a `SharedOneShot` type, like `SharedChan`. I'm not sure where `Future` fits in, but `OneShot` seems to be the appropriate type for one-time notifications.\n",
